data.meta_description: Olympic Games Gold Medalist Athlete. He began his career in 1993 as a professional cyclist with the team Ariostea. But shortly before, he won a gold medal in the 1992 Summer Olympics road race. He finished the 194 km race in 4:35:21, 1 second ahead of the silver medalist Erik Dekker of the Netherlands.
